![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/dfbe3578-3d31-41f9-97e0-207b58056cf3/20240527_170556.jpg)

WWE RAW opens with the members of tongiht’s cage match entering the building.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5d5c464e-e9cf-40ea-9dc9-38037972d0e3/Screenshot_20240527-170707_Chrome.jpg)

Gunther says he’s going to restore prestige to the crown and then he’s going to restore prestige to the World Championship. Because Damian Priest stole the world title.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4f755d62-461d-4f5f-b46a-775017900015/Screenshot_20240527_171224.jpg)

Damian Priest says Gunther hasn’t proven anything because he stole the Crown from Randy with a fluke victory. He says he didn’t steal the title because he won with MITB the way many others have.

But if Gunther doesn’t know how things work, Priest can teach him. Gunther says he’s been waiting since he got here for someone to teach him anything.

Gunther wants to teach Priest something about this sport that he loves.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e818825c-3b37-45e5-8b47-720972801cca/Screenshot_20240527_171523.jpg)

Drew McIntyre interrupts to remind them who’s the number 1 contender.

CM Punk chants break out but Drew says Punk is lucky he got injured because he probably would’ve been fired by now and he’s got nowhere else to go.

Drew turns his attention to Damian. Says he sucks as a leader of Judgement Day so he better start focusing on what’s important. Himself and the World Championship.

Drew says it’s time for a geography lesson because they don’t teach it in America. (He’s an Americancitizen now, he can say this).

Drew reminds Priest that he’s going to Scotland now, this is REAL Drew territory. The crowd won’t be there for him.

Priest says that won’t work. Instead, he wants to know Drew's wife's name.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7d839ecb-6ac4-4b9b-998b-8ad465adab77/Screenshot_20240527_172145.jpg)

Before they can fight. Braun comes out for his match with JD McDonough

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b32c6f50-25bd-4e24-971a-a045b2c8bc3f/Screenshot_20240527_172612.jpg)

*   ## **_BRAUN STROWMAN DEF. JD MCDONOUGH_**
    

Not a squash match. But a fairly paint by numbers David vs Goliath match. Carlito and Finn Balor jump Strowman unsuccessfully before they're cleared out of the ring

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b68adf6c-4315-4476-96d4-f279c8ddb8ed/Screenshot_20240527_173606.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/be41d8b7-d3ff-4db7-9f2d-0654dda4d2b1/Screenshot_20240527_173716.jpg)

Liv says Becky still thinks she can’t beat her after what Dominik did last night. So she’s requested this Steel Cage to prove she can win. Watch her.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/66e2dcd5-436d-4787-aaf9-87750cacdf98/Screenshot_20240527_174538.jpg)

Ilja thanks Ricochet for saving him from Bron Breakker. Offers him a match for tonight. Ricochet accepts.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cfd4af7e-8a67-4184-b697-a52a82f06b3b/Screenshot_20240527_180120.jpg)

*   ## **_ILJA DRAGUNOV VS RICOCHET GOES TO NO CONTEST_**
    

The suspended Bron Breakker appears and takes both men out.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1c91bea7-6bb8-42bb-8bef-123119b69cd8/Screenshot_20240527-180352_Chrome.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8c4994e4-956d-40de-b913-2c706d86df5b/Screenshot_20240527_181053.jpg)

Miz asks why R Truth has him dressed in all white. R Truth says its to represent his flavor.

Miz asks does that mean he’s Vanilla and R Truth is Choc— R-Truth says Strawberry.

“Why? What flavor what you going to say?”

New Days walks up, Interested in the flavor Miz was gonna say as well.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5cd38288-d55d-4579-8455-ed5d701498dc/Screenshot_20240527_181102.jpg)

Karrion Kross interrupts the moment to see if Xavier Woods would drop the New Day and join his faction.

Woods is offended and challenges AOP to a match next week instead. AND they don’t think Miz was going to say Strawberry.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5322369c-f49d-48ef-a330-38810a4b1024/Screenshot_20240527_181434.jpg)

*   ## **_AUTHORS OF PAIN DEF. THE CREED BROTHERS_**
    

Creed Bros get taken care of pretty quickly by the Authors of Pain.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/47c03ff2-4b77-475c-b803-a7be4d8f58ef/Screenshot_20240527_182904.jpg)

Ludwig calls out Sheamus for being a keyboard warrior who could never beat GUNTHER.

Sheamus goes backstage. Gets jumped by Ludwig and they both brawl back out into the arena until they’re broken up.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c9cb1491-2fc9-4ab8-8d85-158f6f3c5d37/Screenshot_20240527_183051.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b00c03e2-a8ab-4de5-937f-62851d647f9e/Screenshot_20240527_183952.jpg)

*   ## **_LYRA VALKYRIA DEF. KAIRI SANE_**
    

Lyra gets beat on the whole match and steals one out in the end.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5048e847-9bee-4145-b0c0-882bcab3af7d/Screenshot_20240527_184331.jpg)

Priest asks JD what’s he doing speaking with Liv backstage. KD says he was just letting her know she won’t be Champ for long.

Damien Priest finally speaks to Dom and let’s him know that he needs to fix this situation with Liv.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/94b47327-7450-4e18-8958-f828314a033a/Screenshot_20240527_190216.jpg)

*   ## **_REY MYSTERIO DEF. CARLITO_**
    

Pretty good match. Ends when Rey fights off some interference from Finn Balor with the help of Dragon Lee.

Post match, Damien Priest has had enough of Judgement Day's bumbling and failing. He takes out Rey and Dragon Lee himself.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f63ee01e-fbb8-48b0-9c28-a76b4cc137f5/Screenshot_20240527_190346.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/eae8c487-ef2e-4084-939f-3dc478bfaa1a/Screenshot_20240527_190439.jpg)

The weekly Alpha Academy shaming session is interrupted by Braun who’s still searching for JD.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5d599fd2-522d-4a7c-ad74-282225705736/Screenshot_20240527_191434.jpg)

*   ## **_BRONSON REED DEF. OTIS_**
    

Otis is on his way to winning the match before Chad Gable stops him from hitting the worm and costs him. Gable then calls out the rest of the Alpha Academy to “settle this now”

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5ea9857d-5733-4349-a4f0-c3f759a7361f/Screenshot_20240527_191518.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4f5bdc9d-cbd6-42c6-a629-d6c2a5ed99c5/Screenshot_20240527-192036_Chrome.jpg)

Chad Gable is literally going to whip Otis to discipline him. Maxxine stops Chad but he’s berated and kicked her out the ring.

Chad is going to whip Otis when Sami Zayn interrupts

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/55405065-351f-4517-aa36-57117a3dbdba/Screenshot_20240527_192346.jpg)

Sami Zayn tries to appeal to Otis again. He doesn’t have to listen to this. He can listen to the fans or his own heart. But Otis has not grown strong enough yet. He allows Sami to get beaten down and he leaves with Gable.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7f0f52f6-96fc-40bd-b737-1954ab7e4148/Screenshot_20240527_193333.jpg)

*   ## **_WOMEN’S WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP: LIV MORGAN VS BECKY LYNCH_**
    

Rumors surrounding Becky Lynch's contract status loom over this match. The finish comes when Dominik tries to help Becky win the title. Finn and JD run out to stop him from interfering(?!).

Braun finally finds JD and ends up knocking Dom into the cage, that takes out Becky and this allows Liv to retain by escaping through the door

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cd509259-f26e-406e-a633-1b9bbc569d3a/Screenshot_20240527_200034.jpg)